title: China Delight
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Chinese restaurant with a 20+ item vegetarian menu section and a somewhat healthy approach to Chinese cuisine. Veg choices include typical vegetable stir-fry to more complex dishes with tofu, tempeh, and seitan. Ample dine-in section, where alcohol and other drinks are served. Main dishes come with choice of rice - fried rice does not contain egg - and a choice of soups, both of which contain egg.
